data.text: #Barroso: We are proposing …4. that the Commission has right to decide on enhanced surveillance of MS when fin stability threatened.
#Barroso: We are proposing …3. that the Commission carry out closer monitoring of Member States under Excessive Deficit Procedure.
#Barroso: We are proposing…2. that the Commission be able to request a new draft budget if serious divergences with MS commitments.
#Barroso:  We are proposing … 1. that all euro area countries send their draft budget plans to the Commission by 15 October each year.
#Barroso on economic governance: We have already taken big steps forward this year.
#Barroso: 5 priorities: fiscal consolidation; restore lending to the economy; struct reforms;  unemployment + modernise administrations.
#Barroso: Annual Growth Survey for 2012: We need to do more. We need to deliver collectively on our commitments.
#Barroso:  The crisis demands not only emergency measures but also lasting solutions to structural challenges.
